nodes.text: CT-6200/8901, also known as Moz, was a Covert Ops clone trooper trained by Null ARC N-10.

During a mission to Gaftikar to eliminate Advanced Recon Commando Alpha-30, who deserted from the Grand Army of the Republic, Moz and CT-0368/7766, nicknamed Olun, were killed by RC-1136, who they mistook for Alpha-30.
Overcome by the guilt of killing one of his own brothers, 36 said their names everyday, the Mandalorian style, to keep their memories alive.
